[6.125, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[36mcoop:\u001b[0m fusion: claude governs; peers codex + gemini consulted read-only\r\n"]
[6.825, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[36mcoop:\u001b[0m shadowed 2 secret path(s)\r\n"]
[7.425, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.525, "o", "Gate is green (gofmt clean, `go vet`/`go build`/`go test ./...` all pass).\r\n"]
[8.925, "o", "\r\n"]
[9.425, "o", "I gave `Client.Ping` **no internal retries** and documented why on the function — a liveness probe\r\n"]
[9.925, "o", "must report the API's immediate, unmasked state, and its callers (readiness checks, monitors, CLI\r\n"]
[10.425, "o", "health commands) already own their own polling cadence (Gemini concurred; Codex was unavailable\r\n"]
[11.725, "o", "after three attempts).\r\n"]
